Sentencas: Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs) cathode often suffers from degradation resulting from different contaminations, such as water vapor from air, when operated under the realistic environments.
Titulo: Effects of humidity on Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ cathode performance and durability of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In this work, we demonstrate an excellent water vapor tolerant Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta (BCFN) cathode for SOFCs.
Titulo: Effects of humidity on Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ cathode performance and durability of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The concentration effects of humidity on BCFN cathode performance including oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) kinetics and durability have been studied.
Titulo: Effects of humidity on Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ cathode performance and durability of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The X-ray diffraction measurement indicates that humidity has no observable effects on BCFN materials.
Titulo: Effects of humidity on Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ cathode performance and durability of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance change in BCFN cathode seems to be more sensitive to the humidity at a lower temperature such as 650 degrees C than that at 800 degrees
Titulo: Effects of humidity on Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ cathode performance and durability of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: C. A low polarization resistance of 0.069 Omega cm(2) at 650 degrees C is obtained in 3% water vapor, and then the polarization resistance increases with increase of water vapor content.
Titulo: Effects of humidity on Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ cathode performance and durability of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, the electrochemical impedance spectra indicate that BCFN cathode contaminated by higher humidity can be recovered by purging air again.
Titulo: Effects of humidity on Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ cathode performance and durability of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
